BEGIN_PGML

It's given that [` 1 \text{ meter} = 100 \text{ centimeters} `]. Do the following unit conversions.

a. [`` [$m1] \text{ meters} = ``] [__________]{$cm1} [`` \text{ centimeters} ``]

a. [`` [$cm2] \text{ centimeters} = ``] [__________]{$m2} [`` \text{ meters} ``]

END_PGML


